item.description:
Steve Fontaine the Organizer of our areas newest Tea Party group is putting on the their first event and I am hoping the Rochester NH 912 Project lends their full support to help make this a success. Here is Steve's messaage:

We are having our Barrington/Lee/Madbury Tea Party meet the
presidential candidates picnic on Saturday August 6, 2011 at 11:
30AM on the soccer field in back of Dantes Pasta and Vino at
320 Rt. 125 in Barrington. There will be live music and great
fun. The event is free. Food and beverages for purchase. Help
Honey Puterbaugh get elected to the state legislature in the
special election on August 9th. There will be presidential
candidates and state legislators along with the fun.
item.name: Barrington /Lee/Madbury Tea Party Picnic
